			<div class="contain main">
				<h2>Do you Zinio?</h2>
<h2><img width="312" height="161" src="/media/38598/ziniofsjpl.jpg" alt="Ziniofsjpl" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"/></h2>
<p style="text-align: center;">Over 300 popular magazine titles, in digital format! Zinio allows you to view your favourite magazines from any device with an internet connection. They've recently added IndieFlix - free streaming independent films and classic TV.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Best part (other than being FREE)? No late fees!  You can even <a href="http://www.rbdigital.com/fortstjohnbc/zinio" target="_blank" title="Zinio!">browse the entire digital collection</a> before signing up with your library card.</p>
<p> </p>
<hr />
<p>  <strong style="line-height: 1.4em;"><span style="line-height: 1.4em;"> </span></strong><strong>Don’t be shy! Reach out and say hi.</strong></p><br/>
				<ul class="social-links"><li><a class="social-icon-em" href="/about-us/contact-us/">Email</a></li><li><a class="social-icon-tw" href="https://twitter.com/fsjlibrary">Twitter</a></li><li><a class="social-icon-fb" href="https://www.facebook.com/fsjlibrary">Facebook</a></li><li><a class="social-icon-li" href="http://fsjlibrary.tumblr.com">Tumblr</a></li><li><a class="social-icon-go" href="https://plus.google.com/105500955963718700243/about">Google+</a></li><li class="last"><a class="social-icon-in" href="http://instagram.com/fsjpl">Instagram</a></li></ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="colspan-twothirds last">
			<ul class="events">
				<h2 class="events-header title">Upcoming Events</h2>
				<div id="recent"><li><a href="/events/2016/3/16/story-time-mice-2-1-2/"><figure class="events-calendar-icon"><span class="events-calendar-icon-month">Mar</span><span class="events-calendar-icon-day">16</span></figure><h4>Story Time Mice!</h4><p>Let’s gather together to listen to stories, chat with puppets and do crafts! Join this quiet, calm session to explore stories through books, puppetry, and hands-on art. <span style="color:#a7114d;white-space:nowrap;">Read more →</span></p></a></li><li><a href="/events/2016/3/17/creative-kids-lego-builders/"><figure class="events-calendar-icon"><span class="events-calendar-icon-month">Mar</span><span class="events-calendar-icon-day">17</span></figure><h4>Creative Kids: Lego Builders Club</h4><p>Drop-in, free fun for kids 6+! Join us for special challenges and projects, or just build your own thing! Please leave your Lego and mini-figures at home...you can use ours!
 <span style="color:#a7114d;white-space:nowrap;">Read more →</span></p></a></li><li><a href="/events/2016/3/17/story-time-lions-1-8-10-5/"><figure class="events-calendar-icon"><span class="events-calendar-icon-month">Mar</span><span class="events-calendar-icon-day">17</span></figure><h4>Story Time Lions!</h4><p>We are taking over the library as we clap, stomp, dance, shake and ROAR our way through Story Time! Join this LOUDER, more ACTIVE session to explore stories through movement, music and play!  <span style="color:#a7114d;white-space:nowrap;">Read more →</span></p></a></li></div>
